{"tid":1803703,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"占士當選十年最佳男運動員! 擊敗美斯保特c朗","createTime":"2019-12-30T11:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T04:10:07.000Z","uid":147522,"like":5,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"aff993f19f7c141869a6be8dd21014b13b1b9eb0","tid":1803703,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"　　香港時間12月30日，洛杉磯湖人隊當家球星勒邦占士被評為美聯社過去十年的最佳男運動員。<br />\n<br />\n　　今天，美聯社過去十年的最佳男運動員（AP male athlete of the decade）揭曉，湖人隊當家球星勒邦占士當選。<br />\n<br />\n　　占士是擊敗了湯姆-佈雷迪、保特、美斯、米高-菲比斯和c朗並當選美聯社過去十年的最佳男運動員。<br />\n<br />\n　　過去這十年見證了勒邦占士職業生涯的巔峰，他在熱火隊和騎士隊效力期間連續8年打進NBA總決賽，並奪得3個NBA總冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n　　除了在球場上取得了卓越的成就之外，占士在球場外也是楷模，並且激勵著年輕一代。<br />\n<br />\n　　昨天，美聯社過去十年的最佳女運動員名單揭曉，網球名將塞雷納-威廉斯當選。"},{"pid":"b93d6636530555fedcc5e7b7b05b50d35ce976ab","tid":1803703,"uid":52571,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"咁我寧願揀faker<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c8d231cab70d8a9f96d7895cfa360a3ad37c00","tid":1803703,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T11:44:34.000Z","msg":"德國聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=608e727e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=3b78223f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n3. <ins>暫時最後一個</ins> deadline 1/1 <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要3300